      class  CombinedDefaultModule
      This is a module used to handle flat specifications in VDM-SL This module is an encapsulation of a number of flat parsed modules The name of this module is DEFAULT and it overrides the getDefs and getFiles methods of a normal module such that it returns the union of all contained modules.
